OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start with isolated
OL,6,Ffog patches. Some sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping, but showers near to the
OL,8,Fcoast breaking out more widely during
OL,9,Fthe day. The showers may become heavy
OL,10,Fand possibly thundery by the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Lighter winds than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDaytime showers easing this
OL,14,Fevening leaving a dry start to the
OL,15,Fnight with clear spells. However,
OL,16,Fcloud and patchy rain will move in
OL,17,Ffrom the west during the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
